        >
          <h1 class='font-bold text-xl'>Itay Lisaey</h1>
          <p>Software Engineer @ <a class="underline" href="https://www.chordio.com" target="__blank">Chordio</a></p>
        </section>
      </header>
      <p title='brief about'>
        Experienced software engineer with a knack for design, proficient
        in both backend and frontend development, and well-versed in cloud technologies and DevOps processes.
        <br />
        <a class='underline' href='about'>More about me â†’</a>
      </p>
      <a
        href='demos'
        class='text-slate-700 border rounded-lg p-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[.98] transition ease-in-out'
      >
        <section>
          <h2 class='font-bold m-0'>ðŸ¤– Demos</h2>
          <p class='text-slate-500'>
            Made for demonstrating technologies and concept to my team
          </p>
        </section>
        <span> â†’</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href='projects'
        class='border rounded-lg p-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[.98] transition ease-in-out'
      >
        <section>
          <h2 class='font-bold m-0'>ðŸ“¼ Projects</h2>
          <p class='text-slate-500'>Problem solving using software</p>
        </section>
        <span> â†’</span>
      </a>

      <nav title='social bar'>
        <ul class='flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8'>
          {
            SOCIAL_LINKS.map((s) => (
              <li class='hover:scale-110 active:scale-95 transition ease-in-out'>
                <SocialLink alt={s.alt} icon={s.icon} link={s.link} />
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
